<p>Benjamin talked about his work at Stripe and his side-project UIlang.com, an educational tool Benjamin built to de-dramatize coding to designers. Benjaminâ€™s thesis is straightforward; coding helps you as a designer stay true to your vision, while it makes things faster. As a designer you donâ€™t need to communicate your mockups to a developer, neither to rely on the developerâ€™s interpretations. You build your idea yourself.</p>

